<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1891-09-14T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1891-09-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="75" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d75">
                    <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Wharton</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Pacheco</persName></hi>.</head>
                    <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                    <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Department
                                    of State</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-09-14"><hi rend="italic">September 14,
                            1891</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                    <p>Mr. Wharton telegraphs that he is awaiting specific answer to his telegram of
                        the 11th and first part of his telegram of the 4th, and that Mr. Pacheco’s
                        telegram of the 9th is unsatisfactory.</p>
                </div>
                </body></text></TEI>